Crosby, Stills, Nash & Young "Déjà Vu - Deluxe Edition"

LP (NEW) - Vinyl, Atlantic, US, 2021, 603497848027, Remastered, 50th Anniversary Deluxe Edition, 180g Vinyl LP + 4xCD, Heavy Cardboard Display Folder, Archival Photos, Gold Embossed Cover

Crosby, Stills, Nash & Young's Deja Vu, originally released in 1970, is one of the greatest albums of the late 60's - early 70's period. The 50th Anniversary Deluxe Release contains the original album plus 4 CDs in a beautiful display folder sleeve. The recordings include:

LP - Original Album (Remastered)

CD1 - Original Album (Remastered)

CD2 - Demos (Incl. Previously Unreleased Material)

CD3 - Outtakes (Incl. Previously Unreleased Material)

CD4 - Alternates (Incl. Previously Unreleased Material)
